{"id":265,"date":"2025-08-29T13:06:02","date_gmt":"2025-08-29T07:36:02","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/wp\/?page_id=265"},"modified":"2025-08-31T02:57:13","modified_gmt":"2025-08-30T21:27:13","slug":"our-meetings","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/our-meetings\/","title":{"rendered":"Our Meetings"},"content":{"rendered":"        <section class=\"ispl-hero-wrap\" style=\"background: -webkit-linear-gradient(to right, rgba(13,34,64,0.9) 0, rgba(13,34,64,0.1) 100%), url('https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/meetings.jpg');background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(13,34,64,0.9) 0, rgba(13,34,64,0.1) 100%), url('https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/meetings.jpg'); \">\r\n            <div class=\"ispl-hero-overlay\" style=\"position:absolute; inset:0; background:rgba(0,0,0,.35);\"><\/div>\r\n            <div class=\"ispl-hero-inner\" style=\"position:relative; max-width:1120px; margin:0 auto; padding:6rem 1.25rem;\">\r\n                                    <h2 style=\"font-size:3rem; line-height:1.1; margin:0 0 1rem;\">Meetings that Build Bonds, Shape Service<\/h2>\r\n                                                    <p style=\"font-size:1.125rem; max-width:800px;\">\u201cAt the Lions Club of Balasore, our meetings are not just formal gatherings\u2014they are the heartbeat of our service. Every meeting is a space where ideas turn into action, friendships deepen into lifelong bonds, and collective strength transforms into meaningful impact. Here, members come together to share experiences, plan projects, celebrate achievements, and learn from one another, united by a common purpose of serving humanity. These moments of dialogue and decision are more than schedules on a calendar; they are stepping stones to progress, where leadership is nurtured, values are upheld, and service finds new direction. In every meeting, we renew our commitment, strengthen our unity, and prepare ourselves to serve with greater passion and purpose.\u201d<\/p>\r\n                                                    <p style=\"margin-top:2rem;\">\r\n                        <a href=\"https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/join-now\/\" class=\"ispl-hero-btn\" style=\"display:inline-block; padding:.9rem 1.5rem; background:#ffcc00; color:#111; text-decoration:none; border-radius:.35rem; font-weight:600;\">\r\n                            Join Us                        <\/a>\r\n                    <\/p>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n        <\/section>\r\n        \n        <style>\r\n            .ispl-pagination{display:flex;gap:.25rem;flex-wrap:wrap}\r\n            .ispl-pagination a,.ispl-pagination span{padding:.375rem .75rem;border:1px solid #dee2e6;border-radius:.25rem;text-decoration:none}\r\n            .ispl-pagination .current{background:#e9ecef}\r\n            .table-responsive{width:100%;overflow-x:auto}\r\n        <\/style>\r\n        <div class=\"ispl-meetings-wrap\">\r\n            <div class=\"table-responsive\">\r\n                <table class=\"table table-striped table-hover align-middle\">\r\n                    <thead>\r\n                        <tr>\r\n                            <th>Title<\/th>\r\n                            <th>Meeting Type<\/th>\r\n                            <th>Date<\/th>\r\n                            <th>Agenda<\/th>\r\n                            <th>Minutes<\/th>\r\n                        <\/tr>\r\n                    <\/thead>\r\n                    <tbody>\r\n                                            <tr>\r\n                            <td><a href=\"https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/meetings\/demo-meeting-title\/\">Demo Meeting Title<\/a><\/td>\r\n                            <td>Board<\/td>\r\n                            <td>September 2, 2025<\/td>\r\n                            <td><a href=\"https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/wp\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/bazar-side-gst-certificate.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">View